
sequenceDiagram
    User->>+Browser: Open https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/notes
    Browser->>+Server: GET /notes
    Server-->>-Browser: List of notes
    User->>+Browser: Enter note text and click Submit
    Browser->>+Server: POST /notes {text: "New note text"}
    Server->>+Database: Create new note
    Database-->>-Server: New note ID
    Server-->>-Browser: Redirect to /notes
    Browser->>+Server: GET /notes
    Server-->>-Browser: Updated list of notes
    User->>+Browser: See new note in list
